# .claudeignore — token-saver file filter for Claude Code
#
# Files matching these patterns will NOT be read by Claude.
# Syntax is the same as .gitignore.
#
# The hook already blocks common noise (node_modules, lock files, build artifacts,
# minified files, source maps, generated protobuf, etc.) by default.
# Add project-specific patterns here.
#
# Examples:
#   large-fixture.json
#   test/fixtures/**
#   **/migrations/**
#   docs/api-reference/**
#   *.generated.ts
